<Layout
  title="About - imakaraokay"
  description="Learn more about imakaraokay - your karaoke companion"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About imakaraokay</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700">
        <p class="text-xl mb-6">
          Welcome to imakaraokay! 🎤 Your ultimate companion for finding songs
          across all major karaoke systems.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">What We Do</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          We provide a comprehensive database of karaoke songs with their
          corresponding machine IDs for:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
          <li>
            <strong>TJ Karaoke</strong> - Popular in Korea and Korean establishments
            worldwide
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>KY Karaoke</strong> - Another major Korean karaoke system
          </li>
          <li><strong>Joysound</strong> - Leading Japanese karaoke brand</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Features</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
          <li>🔍 Search by song title, artist, or lyrics</li>
          <li>🌐 Multilingual support (Korean, English, Japanese)</li>
          <li>📱 Mobile-friendly responsive design</li>
          <li>⚡ Fast, static-generated pages for better performance</li>
          <li>🎯 Accurate karaoke machine ID mapping</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Technology</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          Built with modern web technologies for optimal performance:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
          <li>
            <strong>Astro</strong> - For lightning-fast static site generation
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>SolidJS</strong> - For reactive, efficient islands of interactivity
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> - For beautiful, responsive styling
          </li>
          <li><strong>TypeScript</strong> - For type-safe development</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-400 p-4 my-6">
          <p class="text-purple-800">
            <strong>💡 Pro Tip:</strong> Bookmark this site on your phone for quick
            access during your next karaoke session!
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          🎨 Custom Gradients Showcase
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div
            class="gradient-karaoke-primary text-white p-4 rounded-lg text-center font-semibold"
          >
            gradient-karaoke-primary
          </div>
          <div
            class="gradient-karaoke-hero text-white p-4 rounded-lg text-center font-semibold"
          >
            gradient-karaoke-hero
          </div>
          <div
            class="gradient-karaoke-neon text-white p-4 rounded-lg text-center font-semibold"
          >
            gradient-karaoke-neon
          </div>
          <div
            class="gradient-karaoke-sunset text-white p-4 rounded-lg text-center font-semibold"
          >
            gradient-karaoke-sunset
          </div>
          <div
            class="gradient-karaoke-ocean text-white p-4 rounded-lg text-center font-semibold"
          >
            gradient-karaoke-ocean
          </div>
          <div
            class="gradient-karaoke-night text-white p-4 rounded-lg text-center font-semibold"
          >
            gradient-karaoke-night
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">
          🏢 Brand Gradients
        </h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-6">
          <div
            class="gradient-tj text-white p-3 rounded-lg text-center font-semibold text-sm"
          >
            gradient-tj
          </div>
          <div
            class="gradient-ky text-white p-3 rounded-lg text-center font-semibold text-sm"
          >
            gradient-ky
          </div>
          <div
            class="gradient-joysound text-white p-3 rounded-lg text-center font-semibold text-sm"
          >
            gradient-joysound
          </div>
          <div
            class="gradient-ebo text-white p-3 rounded-lg text-center font-semibold text-sm"
          >
            gradient-ebo
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
